calculateContour

protected abstract void calculateContour(java.util.ArrayList<double[]> contour,
                                         java.util.ArrayList<double[]> border)
Calculate the coordinates of either the contour of the whole shape or the contour of its border. If you just want to calculate the contour of the whole rectangle the second parameter will be null.

Parameters:
contour - List storing vertices of the shapes contour
border - List storing vertices of the shapes border

applyTexture

protected void applyTexture(java.util.ArrayList<double[]> contour,
                            TextureCoords tc)
Performs a mapping from object coordinates into texture coordinates. If the second parameter equals null texture coordinates will be set to 0.

Parameters:
contour - a reference to a list storing vertices
tc - the image coordinates of the texture image
